My personal vim environment.
Continueously updated.
Plugins belongs to the author.
.vimrc originates from amix the lucky stiff,http://amix.dk

Installation
1. for i in ~/.vim ~/.vimrc ~/.gvimrc; do [ -e $i ] && mv $i $i.old; done
2. git clone git://github.com/wjx/.vimrc.git ~/.vim
3. ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
